=== Megatron-LM workflow overview ===

1. Preprocess data:
     python tools/preprocess_data.py \
       --input raw_text.jsonl \
       --output-prefix my-gpt2 \
       --vocab-file gpt2-vocab.json \
       --merge-file gpt2-merges.txt \
       --tokenizer-type GPT2BPETokenizer \
       --workers 32

2. Launch training (see submit_megatron.sh):
     torchrun ... pretrain_gpt.py \
       --tensor-model-parallel-size 2 \
       --pipeline-model-parallel-size 2 \
       ...

3. Key parallelism dimensions:
     TP  -- splits attention heads / MLP across GPUs
     PP  -- splits layers into pipeline stages
     DP  -- replicates the model for data parallelism
     DP = world_size / (TP * PP)

Current world size: 8
Rank 0 device: cuda:0
